Changelog for obarun-build

In 0.1.5
--------

	- Bugs fix
	- Fix gpg directory creation
	- Start network automatically when use of manage command
	- Always use the last version of package to build a package 
	inside the container
	- Allow to stop the build process
	
In 0.1.4
--------
	- Bugs fix
	- Remove network features and do it by automatic way
	- Remove pacman.conf and makepkg.conf file, use files from host
	- Remove templates/create.conf file and integrate it at templates/create script

In 0.1.3
	
	- bug fix
	- split function from build.sh into divers files at build/ directory

In 0.1.1
--------
	
	- Pass under ISC license
	- Templates/create : fix key coming from new lxc version, install base
	first.
	-Pkglist_base : add applysys package
	
